TextEng: Perhaps I could free you.
Me can maybe free you?
Who are you?
Who is you?
I have to be going now.
Me got go now.
Snow globe?
You show me snow globe first or me not let you out.
Text: 눈 구슬 먼저 보여줘 안 그러면 안 꺼내줘.

TextEng: Let me see the snow globe before I let you out.
How did you become a prisoner?
Why you is prisoner here?
Refresh my memory: who are you again?
Text: 기억 좀 되살려줘. 넌 누구라고 했지?

TextEng: I suppose I could help you if the price were right.
I'll set you free if you tell me how...
Me forget: who you be again?
Me could help you get out, if you give me nice stuff.
Text: 좋은 거 주면 나 꺼내주기 도와줄 수 있어.

TextEng: Me set you free but you got tell me how.
Text: 나 풀어줄게 근데 방법 말해줘야 해.

TextEng: Tell me what you know about this dungeon.
Text: 이 던전에 대해 아는 거 말해봐.

TextEng: Me want know stuff 'bout this dungeon.
Text: 나 이 던전 얘기 알고 싶어.

TextEng: How do I get you out of there?
How me get you out of you prison?
How do I perform the summoning ritual?
How me do summon ritual?
Where could I find the library?
What if the summoning requires a spell I can't cast?
Text: 소환에 내가 못 쓰는 주문이 필요하면?

TextEng: Don't worry, Nax. I'll get you out of here.
I think I'll just leave you in there. Bye.
Text: 그냥 거기 놔두는 게 나을 것 같아. 안녕.

TextEng: Where me find library?
What if summon ritual need spell that me not know how to cast?
Text: 소환 의식에 나 못 쓰는 주문 필요하면?

TextEng: You not worry, Nax. Me get you out of there.
Text: 걱정 마, 낙스. 나 너 꺼내줄게.

TextEng: Me just leave you there
Tell me about the snow globe again.
Tell me 'bout snowball again.
How am I supposed to get you out of your prison, again?
Text: 다시 말해봐. 어떻게 널 감옥에서 꺼내지?

TextEng: How me suppose to get you out of you prison, again?
Text: 다시 말해. 어떻게 너 감옥에서 꺼내?

TextEng: What about my reward?
What 'bout me reward?
Freeze, Nax! Cough up the reward you promised!
Text: 움직이지 마, 낙스! 약속한 보상 내놔!

TextEng: Freeze, Nax! You cough up reward now!
Text: 꼼짝 마, 낙스! 상 당장 내놔!

TextEng: Goodbye, Nax... and good luck.
Bye, Nax.
I should kill you for lying to me!
Why didn't you tell me this before?
Okay, tell me how to get the snow globe.
Text: 좋아, 스노 글로브 어떻게 얻는지 말해.

TextEng: Me should kill you for lying!
Why you not say this before?
Okay, you tell me how get snowball.
Keep your secret, then. It's time for you to die!
Keep you secret, then. It die time for you now!
Text: 비밀 지켜. 이제 너 죽을 시간!

TextEng: What does all this have to do with finding the snow globe?
Text: 이게 스노 글로브 찾는 거랑 무슨 상관이야?

TextEng: Get to the point, Nax.
Quit stalling and spill your guts... or I'll spill them for you!
Text: 그만 시간 끌고 다 털어놔... 안 그러면 내가 창자를 털어줄게!

TextEng: What this got do with finding snowball?
Text: 이거 눈 구슬 찾는 거랑 무슨 상관?

TextEng: Hurry and get to point.
Stop stalling and spill you guts... or me spill them for you!
Text: 시간 끌지 말고 다 말해... 안 그러면 나 네 배 갈라!

TextEng: Where can I find these gongs?
Where me find gongs?
Thanks for the info. You can go now.
Me thank you for info. You go now.
Thanks for the info. Guess it's time to kill you now.
Text: 정보 고마워. 이제 널 죽일 시간인 것 같군.

TextEng: Me thank you for info. Me kill you now.
Me already got snow globe. You need give me other reward.
Text: 나 이미 눈 구슬 있어. 다른 상 줘야 해.

TextEng: I already got the snow globe. You better come up with another reward.
Text: 스노 글로브는 이미 있어. 다른 보상을 줘야겠는데.

TextEng: Me gonna just kill you now!
I think I'll just kill you instead.
Text: 그냥 널 죽이는 게 나을 것 같아.

TextEng: Okay. You go now. Me not need reward.
Text: 알았어. 이제 가. 나 상 필요 없어.

TextEng: Fine. I guess I don't need a reward. Get out of here.
Text: 좋아. 보상은 필요 없어. 어서 가.

TextEng: Me already got snow globe. You better give me other stuff.
Text: 나 이미 눈 구슬 있어. 다른 거 줘야 해.

TextEng: I already went and got the snow globe. You better come up with something else.
Text: 스노 글로브는 이미 가져왔어. 다른 거 줘야겠는데.
